snippet.title: Sniper Killer - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2389570/Sniper_Killer/

A new game from Jordan King & Henry Hoare 

You're the madman named THE SNIPER KILLER! Terrorize the city with your keen eye and thirst for blood while staying one step ahead of a detective hell bent on bringing you to justice.
